data.title: Top 500 Classic Rock Songs of All Time
meta_keywords: top classic rock songs of all time
data.meta_description: This Memorial Day Weekend, the Home of Rock and Roll conducted its annual countdown of the top 500 songs of all time. This year's #1 pick caused quite a stir. Here's the full list for anyone who wants to see where their favorite song wound up on the ultimate list.
data.text:
This Memorial Day Weekend, the Home of Rock and Roll conducted its annual countdown of the top 500 songs of all time. The countdown also coincided with the 45th anniversary of the first time WPDH signed on the air as a rock station in the Hudson Valley. This year's #1 pick caused quite a stir. Here's the full list for anyone who wants to see where their favorite song wound up on the ultimate list.

2. QUEEN - Bohemian Rhapsody

3. PINK FLOYD - Another Brick In The Wall(Pt II)
